message.content: cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.NEURON - The paper deals with the application of deep learning algorithms for the identification of Crohn's disease in Magnetic Resonance Enterography images. This involves image analysis and classification, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) sub-categories. The paper also deals with a medical application, which could fall under the medical imaging (cs.MED) sub-category. Finally, the paper employs soft attention mechanisms, which could fall under the neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NEURON) sub-category.
